{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-agreement-or-disagreement/task-17","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-agreement-or-disagreement","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-agreement-or-disagreement/task-17"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Da li se Brian slaže sa predlogom Sare o prioritetu za mrežu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Da, on se potpuno slaže i želi samo pažnju za mrežu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Brian predlaže rešenje po dogovoru za jednaku raspodelu resursa za obe platforme, a ne samo za mrežu.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ne, on odbija i samo predlaže za aplikaciju za telefon</p>","feedback":"<p>Odgovor Braiana nije direktno negiranje; on predlaže balansiran pristup umesto da se fokusira samo na mobilnu aplikaciju.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Dogovorio se sa Sarom, ali predlaže dogovor s jednakim prioritetima za obe platforme</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Saglašava se, ali predlaže odlaganje odluke za kasnije</p>","feedback":"<p>Predlog Brajana je brz i specifičan o raspodeli resursa po jednakosti, nije odlaganje odluke.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0},{"character":"Brian","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"8.3-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":7.22,"finishTimestamp":25.2},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"charact